    "description": "Yum! Brands India is actively seeking a talented and motivated Guest Relations Manager to join our dynamic team in Bhubaneswar. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Yum! Brands India:\nYum! Brands India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Monitor F&B service quality and maintain hygiene standards\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Manage procurement of hotel supplies and control operating costs\n• Manage front office operations including check-in/check-out\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in HACCP\n• Proficiency in Customer Relations\n• Proficiency in Tour Planning\n• Proficiency in Barista Skills\n• Proficiency in Event Management\n• Proficiency in F&B Service\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in Housekeeping Standards\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Referral bonus program\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhubaneswar, Odisha, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Yum! Brands India!",
